  "texts": [
    "The classification kept the students more involved in the learning process, by allowing them to create questions in a more natural context as they worked through the GPT-3 evaluations.",
    "Aim Main contributions Do We Still Need Human Assessors?",
    "Prompt-Based GPT-3 User Simulation in Conversational AI.",
    "To construct a synthetic data set in German, using GPT-3 based on human instructions.",
    "The questions were consciously selected to be used as instructions, in such a way that the labels on the naturalistic data set were applied to the synthetic results of GPT-3."
